<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sign Up for Event Notifications</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f7fa;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .email-wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #f5f7fa;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5890F1 0%, #4a7bc8 100%);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        .logo-container {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 120px;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .content h2 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 0 0 20px 0;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .content p {
            margin: 0 0 20px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555555;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        .highlight {
            background-color: #fff4e6;
            border-left: 4px solid #5890F1;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .highlight p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 35px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 16px 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5890F1 0%, #4a7bc8 100%);
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(88, 144, 241, 0.3);
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(88, 144, 241, 0.4);
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .info-box ul {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
            color: #555555;
        }
        .info-box li {
            margin: 8px 0;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 8px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #5890F1;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .footer-logo {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer-logo img {
            max-width: 100px;
            height: auto;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        .expiry-notice {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #856404;
        }
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            .header {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            .button {
                padding: 14px 30px;
                font-size: 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-container">
            <div class="header">
                <div class="logo-container">
                    <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="ACM Logo" class="logo">
                </div>
                <h1>Join ACM Event Notifications</h1>
            </div>
            
            <div class="content">
                <h2>Welcome to ACM EventHub!</h2>
                
                <p>Thank you for your interest in staying updated with our events. We're excited to have you join our community!</p>
                
                <div class="highlight">
                    <p>üìß Complete your registration to receive notifications about upcoming events, workshops, and opportunities.</p>
                </div>
                
                <p>By signing up, you'll receive:</p>
                
                <div class="info-box">
                    <ul>
                        <li>üìÖ <strong>Event Notifications</strong> - Stay informed about upcoming ACM events</li>
                        <li>üéì <strong>Workshop Announcements</strong> - Learn about educational opportunities</li>
                        <li>üîî <strong>Important Updates</strong> - Get timely information about event changes</li>
                        <li>üéØ <strong>Registration Reminders</strong> - Never miss a deadline</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <p>Click the button below to complete your registration and start receiving notifications:</p>
                
                <div class="button-container">
                    <a href="{{link}}" class="button">Complete Registration</a>
                </div>
                
                <div class="expiry-notice">
                    ‚è∞ <strong>Important:</strong> This link will expire in 1 hour for security reasons. If you didn't request this email, you can safely ignore it.
                </div>
                
                <p style="margin-top: 25px; font-size: 14px; color: #6c757d;">
                    If the button doesn't work, you can copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
                    <a href="{{link}}" style="color: #5890F1; word-break: break-all;">{{link}}</a>
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="footer">
                <p><strong>ACM Gettysburg College</strong></p>
                <p>Stay connected with our community of computer science enthusiasts!</p>
                <p>
                    Questions? Contact us at 
                    <a href="mailto:gburgacm01@gmail.com">gburgacm01@gmail.com</a>
                </p>
                <div class="footer-logo">
                    <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="ACM Logo">
                </div>
                <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #adb5bd;">
                    ¬© 2024 ACM Gettysburg College. All rights reserved.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
